special_powers.name: MINION: WAIT TO SHOOT TILL I TELL YA
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Nick Fury is within 8 squares, Howling Commando can use Ranged Combat Expert.

special_powers.name: MINION: CUT OFF ONE LIMB
special_powers.description: If a friendly character of 40 or more points and with the Hydra keyword is within 8 squares when this character is KO'd, you may deal one of those characters 1 unavoidable damage. If you do, place a #003 Hydra Agent in your starting area.

special_powers.name: MINION: REMEMBER YOUR EMERGENCY TRAINING!
special_powers.description: If a friendly character with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword and a higher point value is within 8 squares, S.H.I.E.L.D. Specialist can use Support.

special_powers.name: REMEMBER YOUR INFILTRATION TRAINING!
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword and a higher point value is within 8 squares, S.H.I.E.L.D. Agent can use Stealth.

special_powers.name: SPY TO THE CORE
special_powers.description: Black Widow can use Stealth.

special_powers.name: TRADING PLACES
special_powers.description: When Adaptoid hits a single-base character with a close combat attack, after actions resolve Adaptoid and the hit character may be placed in each other's squares.

special_powers.name: ABSORBING THE ENVIRONMENT
special_powers.description: Whenever Stonewall occupies clear terrain, he can use Toughness.  Whenever Stonewall occupies hindering terrain, he can use Invulnerability.

special_powers.name: BOUNCEBACK
special_powers.description: Slingshot can use Hypersonic Speed.  When she uses it, after actions resolve, deal her 1 unavoidable damage if she does not occupy the square she occupied when given the power action.

special_powers.name: MENTAL RADAR SENSE
special_powers.description: Mentallo ignores other character's Stealth.

special_powers.name: WELL-BALANCED ATTACK
special_powers.description: Diamondback can use Running Shot.  If she uses it and hits, after actions resolve she may move up to two squares as a free action.

special_powers.name: BULLETPROOF SKIN
special_powers.description: Luke Cage can use Willpower and Toughness. When a character attacks Luke Cage with a ranged combat attack, he can use Invulnerability instead of Toughness.

special_powers.name: SUPREME HYDRA, FOR NOW
special_powers.description: Once during your turn as a free action, choose the highest point friendly character with the HYDRA keyword. The chosen character can use Mastermind until your next turn, but only to deal damage to characters with the HYDRA keyword or team ability.

special_powers.name: S.H.I.E.L.D. DIRECTOR, FOR NOW
special_powers.description: Once during your turn as a free action, choose the highest point friendly character with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword. The chosen character can use Enhancement until your next turn, but only to affect characters with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword or team ability.

special_powers.name: PLAY ALL THE SIDES
special_powers.description: When you reveal your force, choose either HYDRA or S.H.I.E.L.D.  Yelena Belova possess that keyword and team ability this game.

special_powers.name: KUBIK POWERED
special_powers.description: (non-optional) Super-Adaptoid possesses the Power Cosmic team ability and the "Giant" damage symbol.

special_powers.name: POWER TEMPLATE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose a standard attack power that an opposing character within 3 squares can use. Super-Adaptoid can use that power until your next turn.

special_powers.name: ADAPTOID SPAWN
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose one: This turn, modify Super-Adaptoid's damage value by the number of friendly characters named Adaptoid within 3 squares; or this turn, modify the damage values of friendly characters named Adaptoid by +1 when they are within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: GOD OF FEAR
special_powers.description: Phobos can use Force Blast. When he does, on a result of 4-6, after actions resolve, the affected character becomes friendly and may be immediately given an action as a free action, and then becomes friendly to its previous controller's force.

special_powers.name: YOU HAVE YOUR ORDERS, NOW MOVE!
special_powers.description: Nick Fury can use Stealth. When you give Nick Fury a move action, at the end of the turn, remove an action token from another friendly character that was given a move action this turn and possesses the Howling Commandos, Secret Warriors, or S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword.

special_powers.name: HOP IN!
special_powers.description: Doorman can use the Carry ability.

special_powers.name: DOORWAY THROUGH ME
special_powers.description: Once during your turn, you may give Doorman a free action and choose a wall or square of blocking terrain adjacent to him. Until your next turn, characters can ignore that wall or square of blocking terrain for movement purposes.

special_powers.name: BRAINWASHED, AGAIN
special_powers.description: Once per turn, if Sin has exactly one action token, you may give a power action to a friendly character within 8 squares that can use Mind Control, or is named either Crossbones or Red Skull. If you do, give Sin one action as a free action.

special_powers.name: WEREWOLF SERUM
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, you may choose an adjacent character. That character can use Blades/Claws/Fangs, and possesses Battle Fury but can't attack Nightshade. When rolling a D6 for Blades/Claws/Fangs, the chosen character subtracts 1 from the result, minimum 1. These effects last until your next turn even if this power is countered or lost.

special_powers.name: 'LEEPING' KICK
special_powers.description: Batroc can use Leap/Climb.  After he resolves a move action, he may make a close combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: SAVATE MASTER
special_powers.description: Batroc can use Flurry, but only to attack characters that can't use Combat Reflexes or Leap/Climb.

special_powers.name: SOLID SOUND CONSTRUCTS
special_powers.description: Klaw can use Barrier. When he does, after actions resolve, as a free action you may make a single close combat attack that targets each opposing character adajent to any block terrain markers just placed by Klaw. Divide the damage value among hit targets.

special_powers.name: INTANGIBLE SOUND FORM
special_powers.description: Klaw can use Super Senses and Toughness.

special_powers.name: REDWING
special_powers.description: Falcon begins the game with Redwing attached. While Redwing is attached, Falcon can use Super Senses. When Falcon is KO'd, remove Redwing from the map.

special_powers.name: FLY, REDWING, FLY
special_powers.description: Give Falcon a power action and remove Redwing from Falcon and place him in an adjacent square. Redwing becomes a bystander token as described on the back of this card.

special_powers.name: PATRIOTIC DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Captain America is adjacent to Falcon they both modify their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: THE FOCAL POINT
special_powers.description: Steve Rogers can use Leadership.  Adjacent friendly characters with the Avengers keyword can use the S.H.I.E.L.D. team ability.  Friendly characters with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword who begin an action adjacent to Steve Rogers can use the Avengers team ability for that action.

special_powers.name: GENETICALLY RESISTANT
special_powers.description: Scorpion ignores other character's Poison. When Scorpion would be dealt 3 or more damage by a ranged combat attack, she can use Invulnerability.

special_powers.name: BREAKTHROUGH
special_powers.description: Scientist Supreme can use Perplex, but can only target characters with the Scientist keyword.

special_powers.name: SCIENCE IS SUPREME
special_powers.description: Scientist Supreme can use Outwit. She may use it normally, or she may use it targeting any opposing character within 5 squares but not within line of fire.

special_powers.name: THEY ALL FALL FOR ME
special_powers.description: Quake can use Quake. When she does, she treats opposing characters up to 2 squares away as if they were adjacent and after actions resolve, deal 1 penetrating damage to any one character that was hit.

special_powers.name: BRING DOWN THE HOUSE
special_powers.description: Give Quake a power action. Destroy all walls and blocking terrain that Quake could legally target with a close combat attack when given this action.

special_powers.name: MYSTICAL HELLFIRE CHAIN
special_powers.description: Hellfire can use Energy Explosion and Exploit Weakness. When he uses Energy Explosion, he deals penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: WITH MY QUEEN BY MY SIDE
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Storm is on the map, Black Panther and Storm may both use Support, but can only use it on each other.

special_powers.name: ALWAYS ONE STEP AHEAD
special_powers.description: Black Panther can use Outwit. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: SLITHERY DOU
special_powers.description: Cobra can use Plasticity. When a friendly character named Mister Hyde is adjacent to Cobra, they both modify their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: NO ESSSSSCAPE
special_powers.description: Characters using Hypersonic Speed or Leap/Climb can't automatically break away from Cobra, but they add 2 to their breakaway rolls.

special_powers.name: ELECTRICAL DISCHARGE
special_powers.description: Eel can use Energy Explosion.

special_powers.name: CAPTAIN AMERICA'S SHIELD
special_powers.description: Captain America begins the game holding The Shield, Captain America can use Super Strength but only to pick up and hold The Shield. Captain America does not use The Shield while making close combat attacks. While The Shield is being held by Captain America, he can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Running Shot.

special_powers.name: THE SHIELD (LIGHT OBJECT)
special_powers.description: The Shield can't be destroyed, only #CA040 Captain America can hold or pick up The Shield. When used in a ranged attack, Captain America may target two characters and deals 3 damage to each hit character. After any attack using The Shield involves, place it in a square adjacent to a target's square. This object does not count toward your force.

special_powers.name: DYING IS WHAT I DO BEST!
special_powers.description: When Mr. Immortal is KO'ed, instead of being defeated, remove him from the map, place a special terrain marker in the square he occupied and turn his dial to click #9. Other characters can't occupy the square with the special terrain marker. At the beginning of your turn, if Mr. Immortal is removed from the map this way, heal him of 1 damage. When click #6 is revealed, remove the specal terrain marker and place him in that square. Victory points are only awarded for Mr. Immortal if he is removed from the map at the end of the game.

special_powers.name: I'M NO MAN'S PATSY.  OR WOMAN'S!
special_powers.description: The Mastermind power can not be used to transfer damage to Mr. Immortal.

special_powers.name: HIGH-FREQUENCY ELECTRICAL BOLTS
special_powers.description: Crimson Dynamo can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast.  When using it to target a character with the Armor or Robot keyword, modify that character's defense value by -2.

special_powers.name: ENVELOP IN DARKNESS
special_powers.description: Once during your turn, Darkstar can use Smoke Cloud as a free action.

special_powers.name: DARKFORCE MANIPULATION
special_powers.description: Darkstar can use Barrier and Toughness.

special_powers.name: TREACHEROUS DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Mentallo is adjacent to Fixer. they both modify their attack value by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: COBBLE ANY OBJECT INTO A WEAPON
special_powers.description: Give Fixer a power action when he occupies a sqaure with an object. Replace that object with any light or heavy special object you own from outside the game that's not already on the map or being held and has an equal point value.

special_powers.name: GODKILLER
special_powers.description: Gorgon can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Exploit Weakness. When attacking a character with the Deity or Mystical keywords, Gorgon may reroll the d6 roll for Blades/Claws/Fangs once.

special_powers.name: STONE GAZE
special_powers.description: Gorgon may use Energy Explosion with a range of 6. When he does, you may give each hit character less than 100 points an action token in addition to the normal effects.

special_powers.name: INSANE LEADERSHIP
special_powers.description: Dirk Anger can use Leadership. Other characters can't use Leadership. Opposing characters within 4 squares of Dirk Anger can't use team abilities.

special_powers.name: UNUSUAL WEAPONS OF MASS DESTRUCTION
special_powers.description: Adjacent Friendly characters that currently possess a special power modify their attack values by +1.

special_powers.name: IMPENETRABLE MENTAL SHIELDS
special_powers.description: When a target of Mind Control or Penetrating/Psychic Blast, Quasar modifies his defense value by +2.

special_powers.name: QUANTUM TELEPORTATION
special_powers.description: Quasar can use Phasing/Teleport. When he does, if he moved 5 squares or less, after the action resolves he can make a ranged combat attack at half range as a free action.

special_powers.name: QUANTUM CONSTRUCTS
special_powers.description: Quasar can use Barrier, Defend and Invulnerability.

special_powers.name: KINETIC ENERGY DRAIN
special_powers.description: Opposing characters that are given a non-free action within 8 squares of Maelstrom modify their speed value by -2 for that action.

special_powers.name: KNETIC BACKLASH
special_powers.description: Maelstrom can use Impervious. When he rolls a d6 for Impervious from damage dealt by an attack, on a result of 5 or 6, the attacker is dealt 1 unavoidable damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: THE REST OF THE UNIVERSE STOPS FOR ME
special_powers.description: (non-optional) Maelstrom possesses the giant damage symbol. Each time an opposing character takes damage from a ranged combat attack made by Maelstrom, you may heal him of 1 damage and the hit characters cannot be moved during their next turn.

special_powers.name: ALL HEAD
special_powers.description: MODOK can't use the Carry ability.

special_powers.name: PSYCHIC BOMB
special_powers.description: MODOK can use Pulse Wave. When he does, choose a keyword that MODOK possesses. Friendly characters with the chosen keyword are not affected by this use of Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: MASTER OF THE ZODIAC
special_powers.description: Scorpio begins the game with the Zodiac Key placed on the map by an opponent into a clear square at least five squares from any starting area. Scorpio automatically rolls a 6 when rolling for the Zodiac Key. When Scorpio is KO'ed, remove the Zodiac Key form the game. Scorpio can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Penetrating/Psychic Blast while the Zodiac key is on his character card.
Modify this character's combat values by +1 and this character can use Probability Control if it cannot already.

special_powers.name: CAPTAIN AMERICA'S CLONED BODY
special_powers.description: Red Skull can use Close Combat Expert and Leadership.

special_powers.name: DUST OF DEATH
special_powers.description: Red Skull can use Poison.  When using it, adjacent opposing characters less than 100 points or named Captain America are dealt 2 damage instead.

special_powers.name: TACTICAL GENIUS OF THE REICH
special_powers.description: If an opposing character within 8 squares is adjacent to 2 or more characters friendly to Red Skull, modify the opposing character's defense by -1.

special_powers.name: HYDRA SEES ALL
special_powers.description: Each friendly character possessing the HYDRA keyword or team ability may ignore one friendly character possessing the HYDRA keyword or team ability for line of fire purposes once per round.

special_powers.name: SATAN CLAW
special_powers.description: Baron Strucker can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Energy Explosion. When a character takes damage from Baron Strucker's attack using Blades/Claws/Fangs, deal 1 damage to each character opposing to Baron Strucker adjacent to that character.

special_powers.name: DEATH SPORE VIRUS
special_powers.description: Baron Strucker can use Poison. When using it, adjacent opposing characters 100 points and greater or named Nick Fury are dealt 2 damage instead.

special_powers.name: MASTER OF THE MASTERS
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character uses the Masters of Evil team ability, roll a d6 that can't be re-rolled. On a 4-6, that team ability does not deal 1 unavoidable damage for this action.

special_powers.name: SHADOWCAT
special_powers.description: Kitty Pryde can use Phasing/Teleport and Stealth. She can use Toughness when targeted by a close combat attack.

special_powers.name: OUT OF THE WALLS
special_powers.description: Kitty Pryde ignores walls for adjacency purposes when making close combat attacks.

special_powers.name: MASSIVE DISRUPTION
special_powers.description: When Kitty Pryde moves due to her own action, after actions resolve you may remove from the map any objects occupying her square, an adjacent square, or being held by an adjacent character.

special_powers.name: MONKEY JOE
special_powers.description: Squirrel Girl begins the game with Monkey Joe attached.  While Monkey Joe is attached, Squirrel Girl can use Super Senses.  When Monkey Joe is KO'd, reattach him to Squirrel Girl.  When Squirrel Girl is KO'd, remove Monkey Joe from the map.

special_powers.name: RUN, MONKEY JOE, RUN!
special_powers.description: Give Squirrel Girl a power action and remove Monkey Joe from Squirrel Girl and place him in adjacent square.  Monkey Joe becomes a bystander token as described on the back of this card.

special_powers.name: INVISIBLE BARRIER
special_powers.description: Invisible Woman begins the game without the Invisible Barrier. If the Invisible Barrier is attached, Invisible Woman and adjacent friendly characters can use Energy Shield/Deflection. The Invisible Barrier remains attached to Invisible Woman until she takes damage from an opponent's attack.

special_powers.name: SHIELDS UP!
special_powers.description: Invisible Woman can use Barrier. When she does so, attach the Invisible Barrier to her after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: YOU CAN'T SEE WHAT I'M ABOUT TO DO TO YOU...
special_powers.description: Invisible Woman can use Force Blast, Penetrating/Psychic Blast and Telekinesis. If the Invisible Barrier is attached, modify her range value by +2.

special_powers.name: NOVA FLAME
special_powers.description: Human Torch begins the game without the Nova Flame. If the Nova Flame is attached, he can use Poison and modifies his damage value by +1. The Nova Flame remains attached to Human Torch until he takes damage from an attack.

special_powers.name: NOVA BLAST
special_powers.description: Give Human Torch a power action that places two action tokens on him. Human Torch can use Pulse Wave as a free action, but the damage value becomes 3 instead of 1, if a line of fire can be drawn to 2 or more other characters. Attach the Nova Flame to him when this action resolves.

special_powers.name: FIERY CORONA
special_powers.description: Human Torch can use Energy Shield/Deflection. If the Nova Flame is attached, Human Torch can also use Toughness.

special_powers.name: BREAKING OUT OF THE TANK
special_powers.description: Tank is attached, Weapon X can't be moved, placed, targeted, assigned an action, or damaged and at the begining of your turn, turn this dial once to the right. As long as the Fluid Tank is attached, any opposing character occupying an adjacent square may be given a power action to turn the dial once to the left. When click #5 is revealed, remove the Fluid Tank. At the beginning of your turn, if you control no other friendly characters, click Weapon X to click #5 and remove the Fluid Tank.

special_powers.name: THAWING FROM THE ICE
special_powers.description: Captain America begins the game with the Ice Sheath attached. As long as the Ice Sheath is attached, Captain America can't be moved, placed, targeted, assigned an action, or damaged and at the begining of your turn, turn this dial once to the right. As long as the Ice Sheath is attached, any opposing characters occupuing an adjacent square may be given a power action to turn the dial once to the left. When Click #5 is revealed, remove the Ice Sheath. At the beginning of your turn, if you control no other friendly characters, click captain America to click #5 and remove the Ice Sheath.

special_powers.name: SECOND DEFLECTION
special_powers.description: When Captain America targets a character with a ranged combat attack, he may target an additional character within 3 squares and line of fire from the first character and divide the damage between them. The second character does not have to be withing Captain America's Range or Line of Fire.

special_powers.name: KING OF THE WEREWOLVES
special_powers.description: Capwolf can use Leadership. When he does and rolls a 6, in addition to the normal effects you may remove an action token from himself or an adjacent character with the Animal keyword.

special_powers.name: LIVING IN HARMONY WITH NATURE
special_powers.description: Rojhaz can use Stealth, ignores other character's Stealth, and ignores hindering terrain for movement purposes.

special_powers.name: I CAN TRACK ANYTHING
special_powers.description: Give Rojhaz a power action and choose an opposing character within 3 squares and line of fire.  That character can't use Stealth this turn.

special_powers.name: LIFE MODEL DECOY
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character named Nick Fury would be KO'd by an opponent's attack, instead of being defeated, you may turn his dial to his last non-KO click and KO this figure instead. If you do, place that Nick Fury in this square.

special_powers.name: SOVIET DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Black Widow is adjacent to Red Guardian, they both modify their Attack Values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: I'M REALLY GOOD AT HIDING BEHIND OTHERS
special_powers.description: Lines of fire drawn to Bob, Agent of Hydra are blocked if he's adjacent to a friendly character that's either 150 points or more or named Deadpool.

special_powers.name: COWARDICE IS MY ATTACK! YOUR DEATH IS MY VICTORY!
special_powers.description: As long as Bob, Agent of Hydra is not within 3 squares of an opposing character, he can use Probability Control, but only during an opponent's turn.

special_powers.name: THE HEART AND SOUL
special_powers.description: Other friendly characters with the Howling Commandos or SHIELD keyword modify their speed values by +1.

special_powers.name: BRAINS! THEY'RE WHAT'S FOR DINNER!
special_powers.description: "Successful" Dirk Anger can use Steal Energy, but he heals equal to the amount of damage taken by the opposing character instead of 1.

special_powers.name: PSYCHEDELIC PRESENCE
special_powers.description: Madame Hydra can use Perplex. She can use it normally, or if she targets a friendly character with the HYDRA keyword or possessing the HYDRA Team Ability, she can modify a combat value by +2, except damage.

special_powers.name: STEVE, IS THAT YOU?
special_powers.description: Red Skull can use Perplex and Shape Change.

special_powers.name: KILLER DUO
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Crossbones is adjacent to Sin, they both modify their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.
Modify this character's range value by +2 and this character can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

Orange squares are the edge of the Helicarrier squares. At the end of each turn, if a character that can't use the Flight ability is occupying one of these squares, place them in the nearest non-orange square that they could be placed in and give them an action token.

special_powers.name: Stair Squares
special_powers.description: If you are using map S-4, you may give a character occupying this square a power action and place them in the corresponding square on that map. If that square is occupied, place the character in the nearest square they could be placed in.

special_powers.name: Balcony Below Squares
special_powers.description: If you are using map S-4, you may give a character occupying this square a power action and roll a d6, adding 1 to the result if they can use the Flight ability. On a result of 4-6 place them in the corresponding square on that map. If that square is occupied, place the character in the nearest square they could be placed in.

Orange squares are the edge of the Helicarrier squares. At the end of each turn, if a character that can't use the Flight ability is occupying one of these squares, place them in the nearest non-orange square that they could be placed in and give them an action token.

Orange squares are 10,000 feet below squares. Characters can't move into or occupy these squares. If a character's knock back path is stopped by one of these squares, deal that character an additional 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: Stair Squares
special_powers.description: If you are using map S-2, you may give a character occupying this square a power action and place them in the corresponding square on that map. If that square is occupied, place the character in the nearest square they could be placed in.

special_powers.name: Balcony Below Squares
special_powers.description: If you are using map S-2, you may give a character occupying this square a power action and roll a d6, adding 1 to the result if they can use the Flight ability. On a result of 4-6 place them in the corresponding square on that map. If that square is occupied, place the character in the nearest square they could be placed in.
